lass=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The SAS selection was no simple process.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">It was notoriously taxing, oftentimes breaking even the most <em>capable</em> of soldiers.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The selection for Tier One operators was even <em>worse.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>That</em> was <em>precisely</em> why stress tests were necessary.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tier One was an entirely different world, meant only for the best of the best. If you couldn't survive a stress test within the safety of Hereford, you had <em>no</em> business being out in the field.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">That didn't mean that Simon Riley <em>enjoyed</em> it, though.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Still.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">His job was his job, and it was that time of the year, yet again.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1yP2A3mGKGuNbJc9d1RBc.webp\"></p><p cl